05ACC"> </span><span class="cs46AE26E6">7.2.1.d.</span><span class="csEF05ACC"> &nbsp;The applicant shall be at least </span><span class="cs68EFC440">eighteen</span><span class="csEF05ACC"> </span><span class="cs46AE26E6">18</span><span class="csEF05ACC"> </span><span class="cs68EFC440">year</span><span class="csEF05ACC"> </span><span class="cs46AE26E6">years</span><span class="csEF05ACC"> of age. &nbsp;Provided, That the Commissioner may waive the </span><span class="cs68EFC440">eighteen year</span><span class="csEF05ACC"> age requirement if requested to do so, in writing, by the applicant, to a minimum age of </span><span class="cs68EFC440">sixteen</span><span class="csEF05ACC"> </span><span class="cs46AE26E6">16</span><span class="csEF05ACC"> and completion of the 10</span><span class="csEF05ACC"><sup>th</sup></span><span class="csEF05ACC"> grade. &nbsp;The minimum age requirements are verified each semester that the student is currently attending school and maintaining a 2.0 average on a 4.0 scale towards graduation requirements. &nbsp;Failure to meet this requirement is grounds for revocation of the certificate.</span></p><p class="cs7F45F1B" style="tab-stops:left -54.95pt left -36pt left 0pt left 18pt left 36pt left 54pt left 72pt left 90pt left 108pt left 126pt left 144pt left 180pt left 216pt left 252pt left 288pt left 324pt left 360pt left 396pt left 432pt left 468pt left 504pt left 540pt left 576pt left 612pt left 648pt left 684pt left 720pt left 756pt left 792pt left 828pt left 864pt left 900pt left 936pt;"><span class="csEF05ACC">	7.3. &nbsp;An applicant for a West Virginia pump installer certification shall:</span></p><p class="cs7F45F1B" style="tab-stops:left -54.95pt left -36pt left 0pt left 18pt left 36pt left 54pt left 72pt left 90pt left 108pt left 126pt left 144pt left 180pt left 216pt left 252pt left 288pt left 324pt left 360pt left 396pt left 432pt left 468pt left 504pt left 540pt left 576pt left 612pt left 648pt left 684pt left 720pt left 756pt